reviewText: Videos were grainy- not crisp and clear.
These are the newer, better quality episodes unlike some of the older episodes which I found surprisingly inappropriate.
came in a timely manner, super condition. my grandchildren are enjoying this dvd, and it is nice to know that I can trust the dvd to be clean fun.
Great book series...fun and full of life lessons
something this generations parents should watch. Great education for parents and children .
Great entertainment for kids of all ages (including adults). Berenstain Bears adventures highlight good moral values in a setting that sparks creativity.
love these books and to read them to grandchildren

Classics...love these Berenstain videos for car trips etc.  My four year enjoys watching them, and I am thankful for the positive family values...a win, win for our family!  Sometimes I even seen my nine year old watching over the little one's shoulder...catching a good message along the way!
my son loved these when he was little ... my two grandsons ,,,  not so much!

This DVD contains five 11-Minute episodes from the Berenstain Bears cartoon. Amazon doesn't always do a good job on their DVD episode listings so here are the episodes that are included on this DVD:

1. By The Sea
2. The Summer Job
3. Fly It
4. The Perfect Fishing Spot
5. The Bad Habit
